GitHub: https://github.com/devipapolu/brihas-chat_bot.git

Description:
Designed, deployed, and managed an AI-powered enterprise chatbot to automate customer support and internal information retrieval for Brihaspathi Technologies. Implemented a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) architecture that searches internal office documents and provides accurate, context-aware responses using LLMs.
Handled complete end-to-end DevOps ownership, including frontend and backend deployment on cloud infrastructure, security, and production readiness.

Key Contributions & Responsibilities:
Deployed frontend (HTML, CSS, JavaScript) and backend (Python, FastAPI) on cloud servers
Implemented RAG pipeline using LangChain, ChromaDB, and LLMs (Ollama)
Configured Nginx reverse proxy, SSL/TLS (Letâ€™s Encrypt), and domain routing
Managed Linux server, Git-based deployments, and production monitoring
Ensured secure access, scalability, and high availability

Tech Stack:
AWS EC2 / VPS (Contabo), Python, FastAPI, LangChain, ChromaDB, HTML/CSS/JS, Nginx, Git, SSL, Linux

Impact:
Improved response accuracy and reduced manual support effort
Enabled fast and secure access to internal enterprise knowledge.

